RACEDISPARITY001001	White to Non-White Racial Dissimilarity Index for Autauga County, AL	Not Seasonally Adjusted	Annual	Percent		The Racial Dissimilarity Index measures the percentage of the non-hispanic white population in a county which would have to change Census tracts to equalize the racial distribution between white and non-white population groups across all tracts in the county.		TRUE	TRUE	2017-02-07	419
